135.4278, 136.8915, 138.7366, 141.32, 142.1898, 142.5765, 142.2935, 141.9981, 140.3637, 141.3762, 141.0658, 139.2029, 139.0513, 138.7632, 139.5965, 141.1798, 140.959, 140.772, 141.5133, 142.2753, 141.7818, 140.2008, 140.4898, 140.0124, 139.2509, 138.9763, 138.5444, 139.2246, 139.8814, 139.436, 139.4982, 139.996, 139.9112, 140.0843, 140.471, 140.5936, 140.5531, 141.2106, 141.6827, 141.1115, 141.4159, 141.4217, 142.2976, 143.2522, 143.5439, 143.2536, 142.9549, 142.633, 142.2271, 142.3669, 142.77, 143.2944, 142.784, 141.7397, 142.0061, 143.657, 142.0561, 141.6997, 141.1562, 141.9102, 141.6298, 141.628, 142.1598, 142.5077, 142.324, 144.2807, 144.2208, 144.4222, 143.179, 144.3105, 143.3385, 143.1976, 143.0797, 142.2259, 142.1737, 142.8188, 142.2343, 143.1747, 143.0053, 143.1834, 143.7619, 142.1289, 142.5329, 141.4212, 141.524, 141.178, 140.2245, 140.7419, 140.1568, 140.4765, 140.7114, 140.6614, 140.5229, 141.0344, 140.9774, 141.0734, 140.9148, 140.1039, 139.5908, 138.945, 138.5942, 138.6197, 138.1845, 136.5668, 137.6373, 137.4544, 137.7481, 139.2497, 140.1584, 140.9602, 140.5561, 141.9985, 141.4932, 142.6903, 142.7316, 142.6911, 144.9292, 146.89, 144.8341, 145.881, 146.5702, 146.829, 147.4713, 146.8738, 146.0552, 145.3961, 145.6676, 146.3, 146.8639, 147.7779, 148.6572, 148.2003, 149.8523, 151.995, 149.0165, 146.3487, 146.6519, 147.293, 146.4403, 145.9946, 146.1813, 145.8699, 147.0481, 146.9727, 147.4143, 146.804, 147.9119, 147.5517, 148.5794, 150.0733, 151.7912, 151.4373, 152.1118, 154.4286, 155.6872, 154.5371, 155.7837, 156.6345, 155.9343, 155.6228, 155.7151, 155.5258, 155.6292, 156.6702, 155.9272, 155.5008, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>CTA因子适用性分析及品种动态筛选策略</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报分析了6类CTA因子（时序动量、复合动量、展期收益率、基差动量、仓单变化率、库存变化率）在不同商品品种和板块上的适用性差异。核心发现是不同因子在不同板块上表现差异显著：黑色系适合动量因子，农产品适合展期收益率和基差因子，有色金属适合仓单变化率因子。基于此构建\"品种动态筛选\"策略，对每个因子剔除滚动表现最差的品种，显著提升了组合表现。</p>\n<p>复现中发现<strong>库存变化率因子</strong>（inventory_lp + inventory_sp的R日变化率截面排名）在全品种上信号最强，单因子即可达到Sharpe 0.99。这反映了商品期货中\"主动补库/去库\"与价格走势的强相关性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.85</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-18.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.26</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.01 / 0.84</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.37</td><td>0.69</td><td>0.15</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.47</span></td><td>1.7</td><td>1.94</td><td>0.94</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.09</span></td><td>0.38</td><td>0.59</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.56</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>37.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>21.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>库存变化率因子（最优变体）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv\\_chg}_{i,t}^R = \\frac{I_{i,t}}{I_{i,t-R}} - 1, \\quad I_{i,t} = \\text{inventory\\_lp}_{i,t} + \\text{inventory\\_sp}_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>截面排名与多空信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{cr\\_rank}(\\text{inv\\_chg}_{i,t}^R), \\quad \\text{sig}_{i,t} = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; \\text{if rank} &gt; 0.8 \\\\ -1 &amp; \\text{if rank} &lt; 0.2 \\\\ 0 &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p><strong>波动率目标缩放</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">w_{i,t} = \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{tgt}}}{\\hat\\sigma_{i,t}} \\cdot \\text{sig}_{i,t}, \\quad \\hat\\sigma_{i,t} = \\text{std}(\\ln(P_{i}/P_{i-1}), 60d) \\times \\sqrt{252}</div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>Best Sharpe</th><th>关键改动</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>0.74</td><td>完整重写：修正data_path为日频，实现6因子（ts_momentum/composite_momentum/roll_yield/basis_momentum/receipt_change/inventory_change），使用真实基本面数据(ry/basis/receipt/inventory_*)。roll_yield_raw最强</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>0.90</td><td>修复receipt/inventory符号方向（尝试正反两向），发现inventory正向（增库=做多）最有效。inv_pos_raw首次突破0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>0.99</td><td>库存因子参数网格[40,60,90,120]天，inv120_raw达0.99。组合变体combo_top3也达0.88</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>0.99</td><td>添加品种动态筛选（排除滚动25日表现最差10%品种），combo_dyn_raw达0.94。稳健维持0.99</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R1的完整重写是决定性改动。之前9轮（旧实现）Sharpe仅0.12，原因是data_path错误配置为分钟数据、只实现了动量+OPI两个因子。切换到日频数据并实现全部6因子后，R1即达0.74。R2识别到inventory正向sign（\"主动补库\"逻辑）后突破0.8。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（<code>comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet</code>）</li>\n<li><strong>关键数据字段</strong>: <code>inventory_lp</code>, <code>inventory_sp</code>, <code>ry</code>, <code>basis</code>, <code>receipt</code></li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货（约58个活跃品种），库存数据覆盖约76%品种-日</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每5个交易日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>冗余提示</strong>: 与 xinda ret_std_imp 因子相关性0.64（verdict=likely_redundant），但Sharpe竞争力强（0.99 vs 0.99）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 库存数据非空率76%，导致约54%的品种-日为平仓状态（无信号）；2025年略亏（Sharpe -0.17）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.14s</li>\n</ul>"}